{
  "description": "A close-up, low-angle shot captures the striking beauty of a flax plant (harakeke) in bloom. The focus is on the flowering stalk, displaying clusters of vibrant orange-red blossoms emerging from dark brown buds. Several long, sword-shaped flax leaves fan out around the flower spike, their pale green surfaces catching the light. The background is a soft, out-of-focus blur of lush green foliage and a bright, clear blue sky, suggesting a sunny day. The composition highlights the plant's architectural form and the contrast between the bold colors of the flowers and the cool tones of the leaves.",
